UID:TODbIBD0VpM496SzhjhjK
SUMMARY:Perfecting Your Pitch
DTSTAMP:20260618T044716Z
DTSTART:20260617T173000Z
DESCRIPTION:Whether you’re a budding entrepreneur\, a visionary startup own
	er\, or a tech aficionado\, this event is tailor-made for you. Join us and
	 discover the indispensable value of a compelling pitch deck. \nAbout the 
	Speakers \nDr. Doug Franklin \n“Dr. Doug” is the CEO and Co-Founder of Dec
	kLaunch and the COO of Fresh Tech Solutionz. He has fifteen years of manag
	ement\, marketing\, and operations experience\, including opportunities wi
	th iconic firms such as Coca-Cola\, ExxonMobil\, and RJ Reynolds. Dr. Fran
	klin is also a leading scholar that has presented at more than a dozen con
	ferences and has published in peer-reviewed journals such as The Leadershi
	p Quarterly and The Journal of the Texas Alliance of Black School Educator
	s. Dr. Franklin graduated with a Doctoral Degree in Ethical Leadership fro
	m the University of St. Thomas Houston and currently teaches Quantitative 
	and Mixed Research Methods at UST. \nDerrell Noris \nWith more than ten ye
	ars dedicated to developing business operations and software development\,
	 Noris is currently the Co-Founder and CTO of Deck Launch and the CEO of F
	resh Tech Solutionz. Both successful startups provide services to growing 
	businesses looking to mobilize their outreach further. \nNicholas Mbaezue-
	Daniel Jr. \nNick is the founder of Egis Project Management LLC\, a projec
	t management firm dedicated to supporting entrepreneurs and small business
	es for projects in the industries of Construction\, Technology\, and Busin
	ess Enterprise. He also serves as Director of Project Management for Fresh
	 Tech Solutionz and as Chief Operations Officer at DeckLaunch LLC. Nichola
	s considers himself a servant of entrepreneurship because he sees entrepre
	neurship as a major vehicle to uplift the community.\n\nhttps://iondistric
	t.com/event/perfecting-your-pitch-33/\n\nFrom Ion District
URL:https://iondistrict.com/event/perfecting-your-pitch-33/
LOCATION:Ion – Conference Room 028\, 4201 Main St.\, Houston\, TX\, 77002\,
	 United States
X-CALRIPPER-SOURCE:ion-district
CATEGORIES:Ion District
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT1H
END:VEVENT
